&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;gitabaz.github.io&#x2F;blog&#x2F;notation-as-a-tool-of-thought&#x2F;full_apl.png&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; &#x2F;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;game-of-life&quot;&gt;Game of life&lt;a class=&quot;zola-anchor&quot; href=&quot;#game-of-life&quot; aria-label=&quot;Anchor link for: game-of-life&quot;&gt;
