            d=&quot;M7.775 3.275a.75.75 0 001.06 1.06l1.25-1.25a2 2 0 112.83 2.83l-2.5 2.5a2 2 0 01-2.83 0 .75.75 0 00-1.06 1.06 3.5 3.5 0 004.95 0l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 00-4.95-4.95l-1.25 1.25zm-4.69 9.64a2 2 0 010-2.83l2.5-2.5a2 2 0 012.83 0 .75.75 0 001.06-1.06 3.5 3.5 0 00-4.95 0l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 004.95 4.95l1.25-1.25a.75.75 0 00-1.06-1.06l-1.25 1.25a2 2 0 01-2.83 0z&quot;&gt;
        &lt;&#x2F;path&gt;
    &lt;&#x2F;svg&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;gitabaz.github.io&#x2F;blog&#x2F;notation-as-a-tool-of-thought&#x2F;apl_gol.gif&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; &#x2F;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Any live cell with 2 or 3 live neighbors survives.&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Any dead cell with 3 live neighbors becomes a live cell.&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;All other live cells die in the next generation. Similarly, all other dead cells stay dead.&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;ol&gt;
&lt;pre data-lang=&quot;APL&quot; style=&quot;background-color:#282828;color:#fdf4c1aa;&quot; class=&quot;language-APL &quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-APL&quot; data-lang=&quot;APL&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;    life ← {↑1 ⍵∨.∧3 4=+&#x2F;,¯1 0 1∘.⊖¯1 0 1∘.⌽⊂⍵ }
&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;code&gt;&lt;&#x2F;pre&gt;
